answers.answer: have your blood pressure checked might be a sign of preeclampsia i had bad headaches with my 2nd
Make sure you're drinking lots of water too. Dehydration can cause headaches.
I went to the er a few weeks back because of severe headaches thought it might be preeclampsia but turned out I was dehydrated
